{{DISPLAYTITLE:Soul Blazer:Data tables}}
This page documents the '''data tables''' in '''[[Soul Blazer]]''' (SNES).

==Overview==
Soul Blazer stores game data in structured tables throughout the ROM.
Analysis has identified over '''29,000 data structures'''.

