==Text Data==
===Text Block Format===
Text is stored in a compressed format with control codes.

{| class="wikitable"
! Code !! Description
|-
| $00 || End of text block
|-
| $01 || New line
|-
| $02 || Clear text box
|-
| $03-$0F || Control codes
|-
| $10-$7F || Standard ASCII (offset)
|-
| $80-$FF || Extended characters
|}

